definitions.definition: A forecast of the future course or outcome of a situation based on what is presently known ; a prediction .
A forecast of the future course or outcome of a disease or disorder based on current medical knowledge .

main_definition: A forecast of the future course or outcome of a situation based on what is presently known ; a prediction . [from mid 17th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( medicine ) A forecast of the future course or outcome of a disease or disorder based on current medical knowledge . [from mid 17th c.]
